<DOCNO> NYT19980830.0145 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-30 20:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9676 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-YELTSIN-BOS &LR;      08-30 1147
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CLINTON-YELTSIN-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EVENTS OVERTAKE CLINTON-YELTSIN SUMMIT 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (i and w coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By LOUISE D. PALMER  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
